Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================AVANT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.32,0:00:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很久很久以前 某地有个勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者为了说服对人们恶作剧的魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,持续着旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,最后 勇者终于到达了魔王城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我终于来到这里啦 魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,快不要做坏事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕我拿我当坏人的 不是村民们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就算这样恶作剧也是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一起谈谈就能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,谈多了又会被当做坏人的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你被当做坏人的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,还… 还好没砸到人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.47,0:00:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者飞踢！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你呀 那又不是飞踢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说不是刚说要谈谈了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那么就接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 呃 姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.68,0:01:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,树 音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那… 那么就这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.76,0:01:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？ 这里放魔王主题曲？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.23,0:01:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就是你的墓场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,魔王干劲提起来啦 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.83,0:01:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,为了勇者 这里只有由我来煽动孩子们了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 快给勇者加油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一起用拳头给勇者输送力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大家的声援让我变弱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 即兴发挥的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就是现在 勇者拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来魔王也理解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经是朋友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.82,0:01:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,收尾 收尾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因为大家的力量 魔王改邪归正
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,祖国得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏大家哦 太好啦太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:02:05.09,Back,,0,0,0,,万岁 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.12,0:01:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,V！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样 我们在校外活动上燃烧着青春
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,三年级的部长 犬吠埼风前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是构思了这个舞台故事的能人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,后辈也是部长的妹妹的小树
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜欢姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我最好的朋友 东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,去年搬来了隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是最好的朋友却用姓氏称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是她本人这样要求的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是踊跃助人为乐的社团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我们就是赞州中学勇者部！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================A-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,向神树大人 拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.69,0:03:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 下次校外比赛希望你能来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也很忙吗 社团活动？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是勇者部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,无论听几次都觉得这名字怪怪的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有吗 不是很帅吗 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.91,Back,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fax0.1\1c&H000000&\an5\frz-29.4\move(1496,637.5,1550,637.5)}有\N帮\N助\N到\N市\N民\N们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,午安 友奈 东乡来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 你们来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天的人偶戏超级成功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 不如说都是急中生智啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:33.58,Notice,,0,0,0,,{\fs37.5\an7\pos(1567.5,30)}勇者部五条\N一 招呼要打好\N二 尽量不放弃\N三 要吃好睡好\N四 烦恼要沟通！\N五 车到山前多半有路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,结果OK啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈的即兴发挥真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,负责兜底的我可是捏了一把汗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,身为勇者闷闷不乐怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是这么乐观呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好好 那么今天的会议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:41.34,Back,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(200,0)}给小猫找饲主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这么多没解决的请求呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,来… 来了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 今天开始是强化月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,搞成把全校都卷进来的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,为这些孩子找主人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,把学校卷进来的政治头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是高一级的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,和学校的沟通由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是主页的强化准备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让手机也能浏览
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我会制作移动版
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是东乡 高手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？ 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是虽然和先前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但要比先前更努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好笼统啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话 要去海岸扫除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在那边也问问别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这个好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,主页强化任务完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,而且做得好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,给 久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,第三碗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,乌冬能提升女子力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不过主页强化好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那么短时间内就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,专家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢了 前辈 请吃天妇罗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,喔~ 好贴心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你 下一任部长的位子已经不远啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我只是看前辈吃就饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这么说来 前辈有什么事要说？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对了 要商量文化祭的节目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 才四月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:20.10,Back,,0,0,0,,哇 已经吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,赶在放暑假前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我想决定一些东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,确实 随时做到有备无患是很重要的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,今年一定要成功呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,去年没来得及准备 什么都没做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,今年也有新人助阵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 机会难得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,希望能成为毕生的美好回忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而且必须是娱乐大众 喜闻乐见的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 但是要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这要大家一起想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好 这是作业
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,各自去想哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 再来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:06:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 第四碗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 晚饭要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 还要吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,树吃得真少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是姐姐吃太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.27,Text01a,,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(323,832.001)\frz15.5}标题\h\h： 匹配者审查调查定时…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.27,Text01b,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs42\frz15.5\pos(1095.643,668.143)}犬吠埼班，报告数值。\N全体在高范围内匹配值安定。\N务必不要忘记在期间内\N准备任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果姐姐隐瞒了什么 你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,比如在甲州胜沼时 明明援军不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,却必须命令战斗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,近藤勇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么突然说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我会跟随你的 无论发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因为姐姐是唯一的家人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,把黑板上的三句话分别分节试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.34,NoticeB,,0,0,0,,{\frz-16\pos(959.785,646.286)}咖喱喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.34,NoticeB,,0,0,0,,{\frz-45\pos(564,837)}吃我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,比较像勇者部的文化祭节目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:08:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,结城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是没什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那能请你读出现在讲到的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,手机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,上课时请切断电源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡同学也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对不起 停下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧 不是吧 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,树！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 大家都怪怪的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,树
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,树 好好听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们中了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 姐姐~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这是… 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这一天 我们的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时 结束了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,明明刚才还在教室里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我又睡着了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,疼 似乎不是在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 电话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,画面变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,风前辈 小树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,总算找到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,风前辈 小树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你们两个都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不幸中的万幸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个要是没有拿着手机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这个app还有这种功能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,隐藏功能？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这个隐藏功能是产生这种情况时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,自动启动的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 好方便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这个app 是入部时风前辈让下载的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,风前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,大家冷静下来听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我是大赦派来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 大赦是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,供奉神树大人的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么特别任务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,明明一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事我还是第一次听说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没中 我是打算就这样瞒过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,风前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我的班 赞州中学勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,中了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在看到的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是神树大人造出的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,神树大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那么… 不是什么坏的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 但是 被神树大人选中的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,必须在这里面和敌人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这个点是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,幸亏是个慢速的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,浮在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord3\pos(1023,982.5)}Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那是宿命点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了杀死世界而攻过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,杀死世界是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,宿命点的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,到达世界的恩惠 神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候 世界就会死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界里 只有我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 是我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,通过大赦的调查 你们被判断为最有资质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:13.78,Notice,,0,0,0,,全市乡镇中学 勇者资质报告书 机密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会… 怎么可能和那种东西战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,办法是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,只要表现出战斗的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这个app的功能就会解锁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,从而成为神树大人的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,盯上我们了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,已经发现我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗什么的 不可能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,带上东乡逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,树也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么能扔下姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,树…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我会跟随你的 无论发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好 树 跟我上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,树 着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是被神树大人选中的勇者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是守护这个世界的精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,通过神树大人的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,会把力量借给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,树 闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,坐过山车啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,把手扬起来 表现出战斗的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎… 出来了什么武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,风前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 连上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,风前辈 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,现在在战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,比起担心我 你那边没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,数量太多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 东乡 抱歉瞒着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,风前辈是为大家着想才没说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一直一个人没法挑明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是正符合勇者部的活动目的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是风前辈的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈 小树！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.41,0:20:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 不要管我 你快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么话 怎么能把朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,扔下朋友不管什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:20:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事我绝对做不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里舍弃朋友的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是勇者！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,留下痛苦的回忆
